    "lyrics": {
      "text": "On this day the Vir--gin bear-eth the Tran-scend-ent in es---sence; to the Un-ap-proach--a-ble, the earth doth of-fer a small___ cave; An--gels join in choir with shep---herds in giv-ing glo---ry; with__ a star the Ma-gi trav-el up-on their jour---ney; for our sakes is born a young Child, He that ex-ist-ed be-fore the ag-es as God.____"
